```
Block
```
SNIPPET
```
block(
  pmap(ptR$${1:block}, block)
)
```
SVGR
```
library(svgR)
WH<-c(48,32)
ptR<-list(
  x=matrix(0,2,0)
)
svgR(wh=WH, fill='none', stroke='#00FFFF', stroke.width=2,
  rect(
    cxy=WH/2,
    wh=WH/1.5
    
  ),
  text(cxy=WH/2, 'B', fill='#00FFFF')
)
```
